{"tid":1528573,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【和理非、文宣組請進場】十一奉獻支持呢場運動","createTime":"2019-09-01T14:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:48:58.000Z","uid":13781,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c77014808cd49b3bc84fdc898b2603c9bb43ce11","tid":1528573,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:26:50.000Z","msg":"咩係十一奉獻？<br />\n所謂的十一奉獻是把我們收入的十分一收入歸給上帝、獻給上帝，來感激上帝賜給我們的一切。《聖經》記著：地上所有的，無論是地上的種子，是樹上的果子，十分之一是耶和華的，是歸給耶和華為聖的。其實我們能夠奉獻，是出於神的恩典。我們把從神而來的，留十分一給上帝，是尊榮耶和華，也是我們對上帝的感激。<br />\n(source: <a href=\"http://www.media.org.hk/tme_main/index.php/ctvprogram/11donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.media.org.hk%2Ftme_main%2Findex.php%2Fctvprogram%2F11donate&d=3Z9ZeYaQzwHPi2iIp4702Dk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=2bc13018\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.media.org.hk/tme_main/index.php/ctvprogram/11donate</a>)<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每個月捐十分一人工支持呢場運動</span></strong><br />\n可以捐去星火同盟、612人道基金、連登、蘋果日報、立場、傳真社、杏林覺醒&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n有咩好處？<br />\n1. 門檻較低，聽落容易接受<br />\n成日話要捐錢，但係又唔知要捐幾多，十一奉獻可以幫大家定下一個reference line。十分一人工聽落唔算太多，又有聖經back up，令市民大眾容易接受<br />\n<br />\n2. 可持續令各組織有營運資金<br />\n好多時大家可能一次過捐完，但隨著時間增長，愈多人被補，燒既錢愈多。十一奉獻可以令各組織每月有穩定既營運資金，唔會突然進入財務困難，方便持續提供支援<br />\n<br />\n3\b. 建立心理戶口，養成捐錢習慣<br />\n當十一奉獻成為一個習慣，你每個月都唔會覺得呢個係一筆額外支出，反而會放埋入去每月budgeting去計收支，減低心理負荷<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">多一個人十一奉獻，就有機會多一個義士打甩暴動罪，還佢十年青春</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位上唔到前線既，趁呢個月頭開始十一奉獻，飲少幾杯珍珠奶茶，睇少兩場戲，幫到就幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文宣組可以做做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推爆佢！！"},{"pid":"5c4bfe63d78dfc49b063867639d33f5b52e66ca9","tid":1528573,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc207e624b63e3e817058df33bb9c4119540e0a1","tid":1528573,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"0b448aaf77a125773e62922da9714ca8f0e99e48","tid":1528573,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"6591f774a67783056f5abd3f64bbb9521fd0e571","tid":1528573,"uid":210651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:39:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d16933834268ddf4cfa203ca6c10b03e81568e7","tid":1528573,"uid":210651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"u"},{"pid":"c147fd2db40011dd126b4d120f3e0f7a34806025","tid":1528573,"uid":210651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:39:49.000Z","msg":"do"},{"pid":"807275887c85bb1aaa1a3fb09eb24a9e430229e0","tid":1528573,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:43:09.000Z","msg":"85"},{"pid":"89a1ad4a6b4b09b82aab65f9c7ef6fc8962a7996","tid":1528573,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:02:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1a0cba7bdef5250bfcdca7a50b61906ef2029980","tid":1528573,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc9bf2139ecdb996b2193ea3492f9725d43f61e","tid":1528573,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2db7700b5d2fb8caa0975f18fddda53421b6de1","tid":1528573,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:00:53.000Z","msg":"星火首選，612，報章次選"},{"pid":"ca803d36391b7433c6f8a76a0f7735a6776be5c4","tid":1528573,"uid":9534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:47:08.000Z","msg":"岩岩沖緊涼都有咁既諗法 幫你推"},{"pid":"e83ce2943f3e49265e7cc3610d9eea023be654ca","tid":1528573,"uid":273354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}